<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Your One-Time Password (OTP)</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>Your OTP for account verification is:</p>
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 5 minutes. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this OTP, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>RTB-14 Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
